schemaContent:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xs:schema xmlns="urn:x12:schemas:004010" targetNamespace="urn:x12:schemas:004010"
    xmlns:x12="http://xml.x12.org/isomorph" version="004010"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
    <xs:include schemaLocation="../Codes.xsd" />
    <xs:annotation>
        <xs:documentation>2018 c X12 Incorporated, Format c 2018 Washington Publishing Company.
            Exclusively published by the Washington Publishing Company. No part of this publication
            may be distributed, posted, reproduced, stored in a retrieval system, or transmitted in
            any form or by any means without the prior written permission of the copyright owner.</xs:documentation>
    </xs:annotation>
    <xs:element name="X12_004010_210">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>This Draft Standard for Trial Use contains the format and establishes
                the data contents of the Motor Carrier Freight Details and Invoice Transaction Set
                (210) for use within the context of an Electronic Data Interchange (EDI)
                environment. The transaction set can be used to provide detail information for
                charges for services rendered by a motor carrier. It is used both as a motor carrier
                invoice to request payment or as details pertaining to motor freight shipment(s)
                charges.</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="ST_TransactionSetHeader" />
                <xs:element ref="B3_BeginningSegmentforCarriersInvoice" />
                <xs:element ref="C2_BankID" />
                <xs:element ref="C3_Currency" />
                <xs:element ref="ITD_TermsofSaleDeferredTermsofSale" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="300" ref="N9_ReferenceIdentification" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="6" ref="G62_DateTime" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="12" ref="R3_RouteInformation-Motor" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="6" ref="H3_SpecialHandlingInstructions" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="K1_Remarks" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="Loop_1-110" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="Loop_1-160" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="999999" ref="Loop_1-180" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="999" ref="Loop_2-10" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="9999" ref="Loop_2-120" />
                <xs:element ref="L3_TotalWeightandCharges" />
                <xs:element ref="SE_TransactionSetTrailer" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_1-110">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Name Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="N1_Name" />
                <xs:element ref="N2_AdditionalNameInformation" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="2" ref="N3_AddressInformation" />
                <xs:element ref="N4_GeographicLocation" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="5" ref="N9_ReferenceIdentification" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_1-160">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Equipment Details Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="N7_EquipmentDetails" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="2" ref="M7_SealNumbers" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_1-180">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Shipment Purchase Order Detail Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="SPO_ShipmentPurchaseOrderDetail" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="SDQ_DestinationQuantity" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-10">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Stop Off Details Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="S5_StopOffDetails" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="N9_ReferenceIdentification" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="G62_DateTime" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="6" ref="H3_SpecialHandlingInstructions" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="999999" ref="Loop_2-45" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="2" ref="Loop_2-50" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-45">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Shipment Purchase Order Detail Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="SPO_ShipmentPurchaseOrderDetail" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="SDQ_DestinationQuantity" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-50">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Name Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="N1_Name" />
                <xs:element ref="N2_AdditionalNameInformation" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="2" ref="N3_AddressInformation" />
                <xs:element ref="N4_GeographicLocation" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="5" ref="N9_ReferenceIdentification" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="Loop_2-100" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-100">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Equipment Details Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="N7_EquipmentDetails" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="2" ref="M7_SealNumbers" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-120">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Assigned Number Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="LX_AssignedNumber" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="5" ref="N9_ReferenceIdentification" />
                <xs:element ref="POD_ProofofDelivery" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="30" ref="L5_DescriptionMarksandNumbers" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="3" ref="H1_HazardousMaterial" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="2"
                    ref="H2_AdditionalHazardousMaterialDescription" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="L0_LineItem-QuantityandWeight" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="L1_RateandCharges" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="L4_Measurement" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="L7_TariffReference" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="K1_Remarks" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="999999" ref="Loop_2-220" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="999999" ref="Loop_2-240" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-220">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Shipment Purchase Order Detail Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="SPO_ShipmentPurchaseOrderDetail" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="SDQ_DestinationQuantity" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-240">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Name Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="N1_Name" />
                <xs:element ref="N2_AdditionalNameInformation" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="2" ref="N3_AddressInformation" />
                <xs:element ref="N4_GeographicLocation" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="N9_ReferenceIdentification" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="999999" ref="Loop_2-300" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="999999" ref="Loop_2-350" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-300">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Carton (Package) Detail Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="CD3_CartonPackageDetail" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="20" ref="N9_ReferenceIdentification" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="H6_SpecialServices" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="L9_ChargeDetail" />
                <xs:element ref="POD_ProofofDelivery" />
                <xs:element ref="G62_DateTime" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="Loop_2-350">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Shipment Purchase Order Detail Loop</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element ref="SPO_ShipmentPurchaseOrderDetail" />
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="10" ref="SDQ_DestinationQuantity" />
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>


    <xs:element name="ST_TransactionSetHeader">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Transaction Set Header</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element name="ST01__TransactionSetIdentifierCode" type="DE_143">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code uniquely identifying a Transaction Set</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Transaction Set Identifier Code" Number="143"
                                DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="ST02__TransactionSetControlNumber">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Identifying control number that must be unique within the
                            transaction set functional group assigned by the originator for a
                            transaction set</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Transaction Set Control Number" Number="329"
                                DataType="AN" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="4" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="9" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="B3_BeginningSegmentforCarriersInvoice">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Beginning Segment for Carrier's Invoice</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="B301__ShipmentQualifier" type="DE_147">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code defining relationship of this shipment with respect
                            to other shipments given to the carrier at the same time</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Shipment Qualifier" Number="147" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="B302__InvoiceNumber">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Identifying number assigned by issuer</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Invoice Number" Number="76" DataType="AN" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="1" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="22" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="B303__ShipmentIdentificationNumber">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Identification number assigned to the shipment by the
                            shipper that uniquely identifies the shipment from origin to ultimate
                            destination and is not subject to modification; (Does not contain blanks
                            or special characters)</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Shipment Identification Number" Number="145"
                                DataType="AN" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="1" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="30" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="B304__ShipmentMethodofPayment" type="DE_146">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code identifying payment terms for transportation charges</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Shipment Method of Payment" Number="146"
                                DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="B305__WeightUnitCode" type="DE_188">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code specifying the weight unit</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Weight Unit Code" Number="188" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="B306__Date">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Date expressed as CCYYMMDD</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Date" Number="373" DataType="DT" MaximumLength="8" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="8" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="10" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="B307__NetAmountDue">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Total charges to be paid by the receiver of this
                            transaction set expressed in the standard monetary denomination for the
                            currency specified</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Net Amount Due" Number="193" DataType="N2"
                                MaximumLength="12" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="1" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="14" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="B308__CorrectionIndicator" type="DE_202">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code used to indicate that the transaction set contains
                            information which corrects previous information</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Correction Indicator" Number="202" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="B309__DeliveryDate">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Date for delivery of cargo to final consignee or to next
                            mode expressed in format CCYYMMDD</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Delivery Date" Number="32" DataType="DT"
                                MaximumLength="8" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="8" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="10" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="B310__DateTimeQualifier" type="DE_374">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code specifying type of date or time, or both date and
                            time</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Date/Time Qualifier" Number="374" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="B311__StandardCarrierAlphaCode">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Standard Carrier Alpha Code</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Standard Carrier Alpha Code" Number="140"
                                DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="2" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="4" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="B312__Date">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Date expressed as CCYYMMDD</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Date" Number="373" DataType="DT" MaximumLength="8" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="8" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="10" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="B313__TariffServiceCode" type="DE_375">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code specifying the types of services for rating purposes</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Tariff Service Code" Number="375" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="B314__TransportationTermsCode" type="DE_335">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code identifying the trade terms which apply to the
                            shipment transportation responsibility</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Transportation Terms Code" Number="335"
                                DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="C2_BankID">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Bank ID</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element name="C201__BankClientCode" type="DE_8">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code identifying payee or payer</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Bank Client Code" Number="8" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="C202__IdentificationCodeQualifier" type="DE_66">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code designating the system/method of code structure used
                            for Identification Code (67)</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Identification Code Qualifier" Number="66"
                                DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element name="C203__IdentificationCode">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code identifying a party or other code</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Identification Code" Number="67" DataType="AN" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="2" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="80" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="C204__ClientBankNumber">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Federal Reserve Routing Code</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Client Bank Number" Number="20" DataType="AN" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="3" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="9" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="C205__BankAccountNumber">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>ID number assigned by bank to its client</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Bank Account Number" Number="7" DataType="AN" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="6" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="17" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="C206__PaymentMethodCode" type="DE_107">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code identifying type of payment procedures</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Payment Method Code" Number="107" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="C207__Date">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Date expressed as CCYYMMDD</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Date" Number="373" DataType="DT" MaximumLength="8" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="8" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="10" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="C3_Currency">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Currency</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
                <xs:element name="C301__CurrencyCode">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code (Standard ISO) for country in whose currency the
                            charges are specified</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Currency Code" Number="100" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="3" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="3" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="C302__ExchangeRate">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Value to be used as a multiplier conversion factor to
                            convert monetary value from one currency to another</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Exchange Rate" Number="280" DataType="R"
                                MaximumLength="10" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="4" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="12" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="C303__CurrencyCode">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code (Standard ISO) for country in whose currency the
                            charges are specified</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Currency Code" Number="100" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="3" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="3" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
                <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="C304__CurrencyCode">
                    <xs:annotation>
                        <xs:documentation>Code (Standard ISO) for country in whose currency the
                            charges are specified</xs:documentation>
                        <xs:appinfo>
                            <x12:STD_Info Name="Currency Code" Number="100" DataType="ID" />
                        </xs:appinfo>
                    </xs:annotation>
                    <xs:simpleType>
                        <xs:restriction base="xs:string">
                            <xs:minLength value="3" />
                            <xs:maxLength value="3" />
                        </xs:restriction>
                    </xs:simpleType>
                </xs:element>
            </xs:sequence>
        </xs:complexType>
    </xs:element>
    <xs:element name="ITD_TermsofSaleDeferredTermsofSale">
        <xs:annotation>
            <xs:documentation>Terms of Sale/Deferred Terms of Sale</xs:documentation>
        </xs:annotation>
        <xs:complexType>
            <xs:sequence>
